{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-awesome-readme-js","path":"/friedger/awesome-stacks-chain/readme","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Track Awesome List"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"d694691b-914f-54cf-81cb-61012a014d98","html":"<h1 id=\"awesome-stacks-awesome\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#awesome-stacks-awesome\" aria-label=\"awesome stacks awesome permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Awesome Stacks <a href=\"https://awesome.re\"><img src=\"https://awesome.re/badge.svg\" alt=\"Awesome\"></a></h1>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.stacks.co\"><img src=\"https://github.com/friedger/awesome-stacks-chain/raw/main/img/awesome-stacks.png\" alt=\"Awesome Stacks\" title=\"Awesome Stacks\"></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.stacks.co/what-is-stacks\">Stacks</a> is a blockchain anchored by Bitcoin that enables apps, smart contracts, and digital assets. Stacks is a layer-1 blockchain that connects to Bitcoin and implements smart contracts and decentralized applications through the <a href=\"https://clarity-lang.org/\">Clarity language</a>. Through the <a href=\"https://docs.stacks.co/understand-stacks/proof-of-transfer\">Proof of Transfer (PoX) consensus mechanism</a>, the state of the Stacks blockchain is anchored against the Bitcoin blockchain, thus providing the security and finality of Bitcoin to Stacks. Stacks brings the programmability of other blockchain technologies to Bitcoin, without the need to modify the core consensus mechanism of Bitcoin itself.</p>\n<!-- START doctoc generated TOC please keep comment here to allow auto update --><html><head></head><body>\n<!-- DON'T EDIT THIS SECTION, INSTEAD RE-RUN doctoc TO UPDATE --><html><head></head><body>\n<h2 id=\"contents\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#contents\" aria-label=\"contents permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Contents</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#apps\">Apps</a>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#wallets\">Wallets</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#stacks-web-applications\">Stacks Web Applications</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><a href=\"#clarity-resources\">Clarity Resources</a>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#developer-tools\">Developer Tools</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#libraries\">Libraries</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#contracts\">Contracts</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#non-fungible-tokens\">Non-Fungible Tokens</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#fungible-tokens\">Fungible Tokens</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#stacking\">Stacking</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><a href=\"#app-development\">App Development</a>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#frontend-libraries\">Frontend Libraries</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#cli\">CLI</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#storage\">Storage</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><a href=\"#learning-resources\">Learning Resources</a>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#documentation\">Documentation</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#videos\">Videos</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><a href=\"#community\">Community</a></li>\n</ul>\n<!-- END doctoc generated TOC please keep comment here to allow auto update --><html><head></head><body>\n<h2 id=\"apps\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#apps\" aria-label=\"apps permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Apps</h2>\n<h3 id=\"wallets\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#wallets\" aria-label=\"wallets permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Wallets</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.hiro.so/wallet/install-desktop\">Stacks Wallet for Desktop</a> - Desktop wallet application for managing STX and stacking individually or in pools.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.hiro.so/wallet/install-web\">Stacks Wallet for Web</a> - Web wallet for connecting to Stacks web applications.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.secretkeylabs.com/\">Xverse Wallet</a> - Mobile wallet application for managing STX and stacking.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"stacks-web-applications\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#stacks-web-applications\" aria-label=\"stacks web applications permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Stacks Web Applications</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://explorer.stacks.co/?chain=mainnet\">Stacks Explorer</a> - An application for reviewing transactions on the Stacks blockchain.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://boom.money\">Boom.money</a> - A web wallet focused on NFTs, and custom tokens.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://sendstx.com/\">Send Many</a> - An application to send STX to many recipients in one transaction.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://miamining.com/\">MIA Block explorer</a> - A web application to exolore MIA coin transactions for all and personal accounts.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://speed-spend.org\">Speed Spend</a> - A suite of working Clarity experiments on testnet (<a href=\"https://github.com/friedger/speed-spend\">source</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/friedger/speed-spend\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">6</span></span></a>).</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"clarity-resources\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#clarity-resources\" aria-label=\"clarity resources permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\