tive;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">21</span></span></a> - A tool for writing TypeScript code that interacts with Clarity smart contracts.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://clarity.tools\">clarity.tools</a> - In-browser Clarity REPL.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://search-clarity.dev\">search-clarity.dev</a> - An application for searching for deployed Clarity contracts.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"libraries\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#libraries\" aria-label=\"libraries permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Libraries</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/KStasi/clarity-uint256-lib\">uint256</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/KStasi/clarity-uint256-lib\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">3</span></span></a> - A library for converting values into 256-bits.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/jcnelson/clarity-bitcoin\">clarity-bitcoin</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/jcnelson/clarity-bitcoin\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">30</span></span></a> - A library to verify Bitcoin transactions.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"contracts\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#contracts\" aria-label=\"contracts permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Contracts</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/citycoins/citycoin\">CityCoin</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/citycoins/citycoin\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">69</span></span></a> - An implementation of PoX lite using STX transfers to mint new coins using proportional probabilities.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/psq/swapr\">SWAPR</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/psq/swapr\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">51</span></span></a> - A Uniswap-like implementation on Stacks 2.0 and Clarity.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/psq/flexr\">FLEXR</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/psq/flexr\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">18</span></span></a> - An interpretation of Ampleforth for Stacks.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/friedger/clarity-dao\">ClarityDAO</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/friedger/clarity-dao\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">17</span></span></a> - A conversion of Moloch DAO in Clarity.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/friedger/clarity-marketplace/blob/master/contracts/market.clar\">NFT Marketplace</a> - Clarity smart contract for a marketplace of tradable assets.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/MarvinJanssen/stackstarter/blob/master/contracts/stackstarter.clar\">StackStarter</a> - Clarity smart contract for crowdfunding.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/radicleart/clarity-rstack/blob/master/contracts/lightning-swaps-v1.clar\">Lightning Swaps</a> - Fraud-proof swaps using Lightning Network.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/elbaruni/clarity-election/blob/master/contracts/election.clar\">Election Voting</a> - Basic voting for candidates using Clarity.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/westridgeblockchain/dualX\">DualX</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/westridgeblockchain/dualX\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">2</span></span></a> - A collection of Clarity contracts that implement a DeFi ecosystem for exchanges.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"non-fungible-tokens\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#non-fungible-tokens\" aria-label=\"non fungible tokens permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-